comments: Sister Ryan is a great professor! Her class is super easy if you read and study for the test. She gives out study guides for every test and answers most the questions during the lecture. Easy A if you read and do the work. 4 test, 1 outside assignment and 1 group presentation ( don\'t wait till the last minute to present! )

tag_professor: GROUP PROJECTS (1)  Get ready to read (1)  Participation matters (1)
comments: Gives great exam reviews before tests. Make sure you study her vocabulary review! Know all the basic information about each vocab word. Watch out for pop quizzes, only gave a couple but if you don\'t read you\'re screwed. Concepts are very clear when she explains them. Pick GOOD partners for your group project, bc it\'s a big grade.
